Example:

1. Add a new remote, fetch and check out a branch from it

git remote add david http://github.com/kdave/btrfs-progs.git
git remote
git fetch staging
git checkout -b david david/integration-XXXX

2. Imitate git clone but track only selected branches
git remote add -f -t master -m master origin [URL]

3. prune all stale remote-tracking

4. update
